title: Fleet Foxes - "If You Need to, Keep Time on Me" (Solstice Version)

media:group.media:title: Fleet Foxes - "If You Need to, Keep Time on Me" (Solstice Version)
media:group.media:description:
"If You Need to, Keep Time on Me" (Solstice Version) by @Fleet Foxes from the album 'A Very Lonely Solstice', available now
Stream & download: https://fleetfoxes.ffm.to/averylonelysolstice

Available for the first time since 2020's Winter Solstice Recording at Brooklyn's St. Ann & The Holy Trinity Church. Watch The Full Performance: https://youtu.be/3VB24LYsE60
